and wait for you at night."

997
01:19:34.250 --> 01:19:36.367
♪ "We will create"

998
01:19:36.417 --> 01:19:38.825
♪ "A world for two"

999
01:19:38.875 --> 01:19:43.742
♪ "I'll wait for you the whole night through"

1000
01:19:43.792 --> 01:19:48.117
