01:20:15.708 --> 01:20:16.617
Давай, давай...

1008
01:20:16.667 --> 01:20:22.033
♪ "With me, Lili Marlene"

1009
01:20:22.083 --> 01:20:26.867
♪ "Give me a rose to show how much you care"

1010
01:20:26.917 --> 01:20:31.492
